long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Generic Infinite Runner Offline Game for Google Chrome
Generic Infinite Runner Classic Offline Version (Only 1MB)

HOW TO PLAY:
Jump: CLICK or SPACE or UP or W (Hold to jump higher)
(TOUCH works as well, but the game it's not responsive)

INSTALL EXTENSION
Click the Generic Infinite Runner icon on the Chrome toolbar
and we will open a Generic Infinite Runner for you to play the game! You don’t need to do anything else!
And have fun while playing Generic Infinite Runner game!
